Suwannapat Kingkaew (, born 10 June 1994) is a Thai professional footballer who plays as a defender for Phrae United in Thai League 2.
International career
In 2016, Suwannapat was selected in Thailand U23 squad for 2016 AFC U-23 Championship in Qatar.
